data.description: WELCOME HOME!  This spacious 3 Bedroom, 4 Bathroom Deep Creek Village home was built in 2013 and features so many upgrades!   The end-unit has almost 3000 finished square feet and is ideally as a corner lot located next to the community playground and visitor parking, with peaceful green area in the rear of the home. As you enter through the front door or garage, you have the choice to continue to the first floor kitchen and living area or head down to the expansive lower level.  The first floor features an open floor plan with hardwood floors throughout the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The designer kitchen features a chef’s island, pantry, stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop, designer cabinets, granite counter tops, and pendant lighting!  As original owners, the sellers elected to expand the kitchen area to create the largest townhome floorplan in the neighborhood.  This extra space is realized in the seating or eat-in space beyond the kitchen.  An expansive deck is accessed through a sliding door off the kitchen and overlooks a fenced in backyard – perfect for entertaining and week-night grilling.  Upstairs, the spacious owner's suite has two large walk-in closets, a spa bathroom and extended space – perfect for a Peloton or seating area.  The second and third bedrooms are both spacious enough for queen-size beds, and an upstairs laundry room is super convenient. The ground floor features a huge multipurpose room with very high ceilings – this can be used as a recreation room, a guest suite, a gym, an office – or all of the above!  There is a full bathroom and walkout basement which leads to a fenced in patio area.  So much flexibility here! The owners have spared no expense – with $67,000 in builder upgrades, $16,000 in custom blinds, $11,000 in deck and fencing, and added humidifier for comfort in the winter. Deep Creek Village community amenities include a tot lot, walking trails, and community green space. Conveniently located near RT 50 / RT 2 with easy commute to DC / Baltimore.  Coveted Broadneck School District. Schedule a showing today!
